  Location: /CS-LIVE_ICPCSTAIC/.folds/project.fold
  Relationship: Anchors folds to immutable storage

⊃ Priment (concept): Bond preservation system
  Location: /Priment/.folds/concept.fold
  Relationship: Implements fold-based relationship memory

⊃ AurioSynth (service): Audio synthesis with fold navigation
  Location: /AurioSynth/.folds/project.fold
  Relationship: Uses fold system for synthesis state

⊃ Parallax (frontend): Visualization layer
  Location: /Parallax/.folds/project.fold
  Relationship: Displays drops compiled from folds

